snippet.title: Luigi’s Mansion - Launch Trailer - Nintendo 3DS
snippet.description:
Luigi’s Mansion has finally released on Nintendo 3DS! Check out the trailer to learn all about this remastered title.

Learn more about Luigi's Mansion! https://goo.gl/vu9B81
